Added make lint targets for python and shell script linting.

New linting targets for code quality assurance:

lint: Main target that runs both lint-python and lint-shell

lint-python: Runs autopep8 to fix whitespace/blank line issues:
- E301: Add missing blank line
- E302: Add missing 2 blank lines
- E303: Remove extra blank lines
- E304: Remove blank line following decorator
- E305: Expected 2 blank lines after function/class
- E306: Expected 1 blank line before nested definition

lint-shell: Runs shellcheck on all shell scripts with GCC output format for
IDE integration

This enables developers to quickly check and fix code style issues in the
repository.

/Claude-haiku@4.5
